# Organization — <%= appName %>

Enterprise organization management for companies managing many projects.

## Layout

```
src/organizations/
  services/
    organization.service.ts
    team.service.ts
    member.service.ts
    project.service.ts
    permission.service.ts
tests/organizations/
ORGANIZATION.md
```

## Support

- Companies (organizations)
- Teams
- Members
- Projects
- Roles (`owner` | `admin` | `member` | `viewer`)

## CLI

```bash
my organization setup
```

## Usage

```ts
import { registerOrganization } from './src/organizations/index.js';

const orgPlatform = registerOrganization();
const org = orgPlatform.organizations.create('Acme Corp');
const team = orgPlatform.teams.create(org.id, 'Platform');
const member = orgPlatform.members.add(org.id, {
  userId: 'u1',
  email: 'owner@acme.com',
  role: 'owner',
});
orgPlatform.projects.create(org.id, 'Checkout API', { teamId: team.id });
```
